EBEL, SUPERVISOR LAVERNE STECHER, ASSISTANT SUPERVISOR March 18, 1964 Mr. Joseph Young 1759 Planters Road Jacksonville, Fla. 32207 To Whom It May Concern: According to the records at Woodward High School, Joseph Young, son of Isadore, was born July 4, 1901. This information was taken from records at Woodward High School for the school years 1916-17 through 1919-20. Since our permanent system of record keeping was not established until September of 1919, it is only in rare cases that records prior to that date are located. Very truly yours, La Serve Sinder LaVerne Stecher Assistant Supervisor Division of Data Processing LS:kc EXHIBIT 4 (c) school record of Apple Rubibis identification Form G146-B GPO 943-662
